; Follow the 4 steps from today's lesson:
;   Step 1: Inspect this scene tree
;   Step 2: Select TileMap and paint your level
;   Step 3: Check collision layers are assigned in TileSet
;   Step 4: Move the Player, Coin, and GoalZone to your chosen positions
; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

